# Restart npm run dev after editing.
#
# Easiest: from repo root run `npm install` then `npm run dev` (API + Vite together).
#
# Recommended dev (Vite /api proxy — avoids many browser NetworkErrors):
# Do NOT set VITE_API_URL. Set where uvicorn listens:
VITE_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8889
#
# Optional: call API directly from the browser (needs CORS; can trigger NetworkError in some setups):
# VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8889
#
# Production (Vercel): set this in Vercel Environment Variables to your Render API URL:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-render-service.onrender.com
#
# Troubleshooting: open http://127.0.0.1:8889/health; backend\run_api.bat; port stuck: backend\stop_api_8889.bat
